The soccer results prediction app that makes sense out of stats and performances for you.

Footbe determines overestimated events that you should bet on by using the value-betting approach. If Footbe’s chance of a win is higher than the one estimated by the bookmaker, the event is considered profitable. Betting on those events leads to long-term profit.

We developed unique predictive algorithms based on the player rating system. Each player has a rating based on his recent performance, which is calculated using team results and individual characteristics, such as goals, assists, shots, xG, the accuracy of passes, etc.

The unique Ticket Wizard feature driven by years of statistics and machine learning predictions is a powerful tool that simplifies the betting process for you. Create betting tickets in a couple of steps based on your betting preferences and our predictions.

Final predictions are based on starting lineups, which are updated automatically before the game kicks off. Once starting lineups are announced, the betting tip changes according to the new and most accurate prediction.

In the free plan, the app provides analytics and information on all 15 leagues, including:

• Livescore and live match statistics;
• Comprehensive match preview;
• Information on injured and suspended players;
• Starting lineups, both predicted and the confirmed ones;
• Match result forecast;
• Best odds;

Additionally, premium subscription grants you access to extra analytics and value-betting tips. English Premier League includes this information in a free plan.

